# Creation

Local-first agent operating system. All pillars are first-party:

- **Account** — `creation/account/` — auth, credits, API keys
- **Forge** — `creation/services/forge/` — planning LLM
- **Lens** — `creation/services/lens/` — search + scrape
- **Prism** — `creation/services/prism/` — memory + compression
- **Relay** — `creation/services/relay/` — GitHub + Linear
- **Pulse** — `creation/services/pulse/` — notifications

Do not add third-party agent-platform bundles as hard dependencies.

UI lives in `creation/app/` (Creation Studio — dark terminal aesthetic).

Run `pytest tests -q` before PRs.
